intent.user_query: How many sales included more than 3 different products?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT SaleID, COUNT(DISTINCT ProductID) AS DistinctProducts FROM fitness_db.SaleDetails GROUP BY SaleID HAVING DistinctProducts > 3) AS Subquery;

arguments.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT SaleID, COUNT(DISTINCT ProductID) AS DistinctProducts FROM fitness_db.SaleDetails GROUP BY SaleID HAVING DistinctProducts > 3) AS Subquery;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
